<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="400" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="7.[159,1366,1241,1817]" pageId="7" pageNumber="400">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[161,511,1665,1698]" pageId="7" pageNumber="400">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Like most species of shrews from China, the Chinese Shrew has never been appropriately studied. There is no information regarding its population size or natural history.
</paragraph>
